I waited for him three days.

444
00:35:15,321 --> 00:35:19,826
A ten-year-old orphan waited three days
because he trusted his brother.

445
00:35:20,660 --> 00:35:22,161
But he didn't come.

446
00:35:24,122 --> 00:35:27,041
